article.description: — DJ Horne had 22 points as Illinois State routed Chicago State 91-62 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Horne carries Illinois State over Chicago State 91-62
article.linkText: Horne carries Illinois State over Chicago State 91-62
article.story: NORMAL, Ill. -- — DJ Horne had 22 points as Illinois State routed Chicago State 91-62 on Tuesday. Josiah Strong had 17 points, six rebounds and six assists for Illinois State (3-3). Dedric Boyd added 13 points and Antonio Reeves had 11 points. Xavier Johnson had 22 points for the Cougars (0-7). Carlo Marble added 17 points and Ke'Sean Davis had 12 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
